WEBVTT

00:00.690 --> 00:01.650
Previously on The OC:

00:01.650 --> 00:04.689
There are rumors floating around about certain improprieties

00:04.689 --> 00:07.570
concerning Griffin and you and they're going to call for a criminal investigation.

00:07.570 --> 00:09.050
- Is everything okay?
- Yeah.

00:09.050 --> 00:12.730
I am not going to use my alcoholism as blackmail to save our marriage.

00:12.730 --> 00:13.970
- Are you smoking pot?
- You want some?

00:13.970 --> 00:16.329
It helps take the edge off and I could tell you could use it.

00:16.329 --> 00:19.370
Seth's napkin confession detailing all of his lies and deceptions.

00:19.370 --> 00:21.690
He told me if he screwed up I could show this to his parents.

00:21.690 --> 00:24.170
I promised I'd never lie again when I gave you that letter.

00:24.170 --> 00:25.050
Oh, my God, the letter.

00:25.050 --> 00:27.090
Did you think you can just dress up your bad boy

00:27.090 --> 00:29.010
so your friends can see how cool you are?

00:29.010 --> 00:31.610
The Ryan I knew would've gotten in a fight with that guy back at the prom.

00:31.610 --> 00:32.490
The money is gone.

00:32.490 --> 00:35.330
I hid the money in my purse. I had $5,000 in my purse.

